EndTime.description: The date and time that the user provisioning process ended.

ErrorRecordCount.description: The number of records that encountered an error during the user provisioning process.

LastReferencedDate.description: The date and time when the user provisioning process was last referenced, with a precision of one second.

LastViewedDate.description: The date and time when the user provisioning process was last viewed, with a precision of one second.

Name.description: The name of the user provisioning process.

ProcessStatus.description: The status of the user provisioning process.

StartTime.description: The date and time that the user provisioning process started.

SuccessRecordCount.description: The number of records that were successfully provisioned during the user provisioning process.

TotalRecordCount.description: The total number of records in the user provisioning process.
